    • Event

      Event(boolean favourite, String name, String description, LocalDateTime startDate, LocalDateTime endDate, int daysBetween, String iconPath)
      Parameters:
      favourite - is the event a favourite
      name - the name of the event
      description - the description of the event
      startDate - the start of the event
      endDate - the end of the event
      daysBetween - if it repeats, how many days are between the two occurrence
      iconPath - the path of the icon The constructor makes a new event based on these parameters
